{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c04847c12e","title":"中央关于和平解决西安事变致周恩来电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c187fac6b8","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":21,"articleId":"c04847c12e"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d2158ef471","type":"paragraph","text":"中央关于和平解决西安事变","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"24d6a92399","type":"paragraph","text":"致周恩来电”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"73b16890a1","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月21日）恩来同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"9b06f8c42c","type":"paragraph","text":"（甲）目前局势是日本与南京右派联盟，企图夺取蒋系中派，造成大内乱，另方面是南京与各地左派企图调和而中派在动摇中","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"8a9c024760","type":"paragraph","text":"（乙）我们与西安策略，应扶助左派，争取中派，打倒右派，变内战为抗战","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"344b22a4ac","type":"paragraph","text":"（丙）请与张杨商量立即采取如下步骤","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"0fbbb54b4d","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）争取蒋介石、陈诚等与之开诚谈判，在下列基础上成立和平。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"2d39b715ab","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，南京政府中增加几个抗日运动之领袖人物，排除亲日派，实行初步改组。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"36013c9721","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，取消何应钦等之权力，停止讨伐，讨伐军退出陕甘，承认西安之抗日军。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"d1e6c1ea7d","type":"paragraph","text":"第三，保障民主权利第四，停止“潮共”政策并与红军联合抗日。第五，与同情中国抗日运动之国家建立合作关系。[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央书记处起草的给周恩来的电报。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"527d04cc9c","type":"paragraph","text":"第六，在上述条件有相当保证时，恢复蒋介石之自由，并在上述条件下赞助中国统一，一致对日","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"89c0f1f959","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）依上述条件与阁锡山、宋子文、于右任、黄埔左派、二陈派等谈判。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"477c9c2f14","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）对阁锡山迁蒋至山西办法应表示可以考虑（四）招致一切愿意和平之人士来西安谈判（五）招致英美顾问再来西安，经过他们使英美赞助和平","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"2439420d7a","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）巩固西安军事阵地，使尽可能持久，以待政治谈判之成功。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"5561d59cea","type":"paragraph","text":"（七）对陕甘之黄埔军官，如胡宗南、樊崧甫、董钊等进行接洽。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"9f1fc5be05","type":"paragraph","text":"（八）兑应以共产党代表资格，公开与落、陈、宋、阁、于等，基于上述条件与谈判，调停双方。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"35d42b4d86","type":"paragraph","text":"中央书记处","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"},{"id":"88de673a53","type":"paragraph","text":"二十一日[1]指陈果夫、陈立夫。","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e"}],"page":{"id":"c73cf9dea8","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"c04847c12e","start":201,"end":202}}}},"__N_SSG":true}